{"tid":358097,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［夢想］各位點樣定義「夢想」依樣野？","createTime":"2017-08-13T13:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T13:28:05.000Z","uid":18746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"941e5e1ae76e6183585ae3a95961c22330eac21d","tid":358097,"uid":18746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"早排聽到有個朋友話佢夢想係每年去一次旅行，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令到我忽然真係諗一諗夢想定義係咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我唔可以話我果位朋友既夢想係唔岩，<br />\n但去旅行依啲野其實有錢有時間就已經可以，<br />\n我個人認為就談不上叫夢想，<br />\n我自己個人認為夢想應該係一啲比較難達到既野，<br />\n並且需要好長時間既努力先得到，<br />\n而且努力爭取既過程會有好多既犧牲，<br />\n努力完都未必有結果等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知各位巴絲打點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d70503f5ea1a6570e2bdc089bde0303be8c1133","tid":358097,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:16:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得夢想係你最想得到嘅嘢囉。。。好似我夢想係同自己鍾意嘅人住大屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78736004f6accfbca6521a089fb82fed08f91ce3","tid":358097,"uid":18746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得夢想係你最想得到嘅嘢囉。。。好似我夢想係同自己鍾意嘅人住大屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有無諗過真係實踐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453b205be53979d0ab26e8651098d009ecde128d","tid":358097,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得夢想係你最想得到嘅嘢囉。。。好似我夢想係同自己鍾意嘅人住大屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有無諗過真係實踐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無諗過點實踐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1b6bb4821b6bce518db508de54cee410d26056","tid":358097,"uid":18746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得夢想係你最想得到嘅嘢囉。。。好似我夢想係同自己鍾意嘅人住大屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有無諗過真係實踐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無諗過點實踐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過你至少都起碼有個方向，我自己到依加都無一個好確實既夢想。可能我自己定義既要求高，所以如果去旅行依啲我最盡都覺得叫期望，有錢有時間根本個個都可以，但真正追尋既夢想應該係就算你比左時間同錢出來都可能無結果"}]}